  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  &gt; 18 years old

          -  acute lymphoblastic or myeloblastic leukemia at first relapse and diagnosed within 8
             weeks before inclusion.

          -  Patients in whom a curative strategy (transplant) is not considered.

          -  patients older that 75 years at the diagnosis

          -  informed signed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  unable to answer the questionnaire

          -  psychiatric disorders other than depression

          -  persons under guardianship
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
